CREATE TABLE user_friends (
  user_id INT,
  friend_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (user_id, friend_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (friend_id) REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id)
);

)
